'''''Aqua Kids''''' ({{ko-hhrm|아쿠아 키즈||Akua Kijeu}}; {{lang-ja|アクアキッズ}}) is an [[manhwa|animation]] produced by [[South Korea]]n broadcast company [[SBS (Korea)|SBS]]. In Japan, it aired on [[TV Tokyo]] between 1 April 2004 and 23 September 2004 Thursdays for 26 episodes, replacing ''[[Pluster World]]'' and was then replaced by another anime series, ''[[Onmyou Taisenki]]''.

